headline: Trust3 AI Appoints Alberto Romero as Head of AI from Citi Bank
summary: Trust3 AI, a leading innovator in AI-driven enterprise solutions, has announced the appointment of Alberto Romero as its new Head of AI. With over 15 years of experience at the intersection of artificial intelligence (AI) and data, Romero brings unparalleled expertise in building scalable and innovative AI solutions for global industries.
